{"content":"<p>在Mizuki文章中嵌入B站视频非常简单，只需从B站复制嵌入代码，然后粘贴到Markdown文件中即可。</p>\n<h2 id=\"基本步骤\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#基本步骤\"><span>基本步骤</span></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>打开想要嵌入的B站视频页面</li>\n<li>点击视频下方的&quot;分享&quot;按钮</li>\n<li>选择&quot;嵌入代码&quot;选项</li>\n<li>复制提供的HTML代码</li>\n<li>将代码粘贴到Markdown文件中</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"嵌入示例\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#嵌入示例\"><span>嵌入示例</span></a></h2>\n<div class=\"language-yaml line-numbers-mode\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"yaml\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212\"><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">---</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">title</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">:</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> 包含B站视频的文章</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">published</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">:</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A65E2B;--shiki-dark:#C99076\"> 2023-10-19</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">description</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">:</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> 这是一篇包含B站视频的文章示例</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">tags</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">:</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> [</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">视频</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\"> B站</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">---</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\"># 文章标题</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">这是一段文章的介绍文字，下面是嵌入的B站视频：</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">&#x3C;iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"468\" src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV1fK4y1s7Qf&#x26;p=1&#x26;autoplay=0\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" &#x26;autoplay=0> &#x3C;/iframe></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">这是视频后面的内容...</span></span></code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><h2 id=\"参数说明\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#参数说明\"><span>参数说明</span></a></h2>\n<p>嵌入代码中的主要参数：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code v-pre>width=&quot;100%&quot;</code>: 视频宽度设置为100%，适应文章布局</li>\n<li><code v-pre>height=&quot;468&quot;</code>: 视频高度（可根据需要调整）</li>\n<li><code v-pre>src</code>: 视频嵌入链接</li>\n<li><code v-pre>bvid=BV1fK4y1s7Qf</code>: B站视频BV号</li>\n<li><code v-pre>p=1</code>: 视频分P（如果是多P视频）</li>\n<li><code v-pre>autoplay=0</code>: 是否自动播放（0为不自动，1为自动）</li>\n<li><code v-pre>allowfullscreen</code>: 允许全屏播放</li>\n<li><code v-pre>scrolling=&quot;no&quot;</code>: 禁用滚动条</li>\n<li><code v-pre>frameborder=&quot;no&quot;</code>: 无边框</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"自定义视频尺寸\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#自定义视频尺寸\"><span>自定义视频尺寸</span></a></h2>\n<p>你可以根据需要调整视频的尺寸：</p>\n<div class=\"language-html line-numbers-mode\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"html\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212\"><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">&#x3C;!-- 响应式宽度，固定高度 --></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">iframe</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> width</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">100%</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> height</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">468</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> src</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">//player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV1fK4y1s7Qf</span><span style=\"--shiki-li